<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1509,1788]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,541,1653,1678]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Current taxonomic position:</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="(Lamarck, 1822)" baseAuthorityName="Lamarck" baseAuthorityYear="1822" box="[548,959,1653,1677]" class="Gastropoda" family="Fasciolariidae" genus="Peristernia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="rubens">
<emphasis box="[548,759,1653,1677]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Peristernia rubens</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Lamarck" box="[774,951,1653,1677]" firstAuthor="Lamarck" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refId="ref11267" refString="Lamarck, [J. B. P. A.] (1822) Histoire naturelle des animaux sans vertebres ... Paris. 7 (2), 711 pp." type="book" year="1822">Lamarck, 1822</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Lamarck" baseAuthorityYear="1822" box="[972,1181,1653,1677]" class="Gastropoda" family="Fasciolariidae" genus="Peristernia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="rubens">
<emphasis box="[972,1181,1653,1677]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Peristernia rubens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is the senior name for the species usually called 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Kuster and Kobelt" baseAuthorityYear="1876" box="[443,697,1689,1713]" class="Gastropoda" family="Fasciolariidae" genus="Peristernia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="zealandica">
<emphasis box="[443,697,1689,1713]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Peristernia zealandica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Küster &amp; Kobelt, 
<quantity box="[915,1000,1689,1713]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.76504" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" unit="in" value="1876.0">
1876 
<emphasis box="[978,1000,1690,1713]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">in</emphasis>
</quantity>
[1844–1876]). For a discussion of this later name, see 
<bibRefCitation author="Herbert" box="[334,508,1725,1749]" firstAuthor="Herbert" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" pagination="125 - 129" refId="ref10665" refString="Herbert, D. G. (1994) A note on Peristernia zealandica (Kobelt in Kuster &amp; Kobelt, 1876) (Gastropoda: Fasciolariidae). Journal of Conchology, 35 (2), 125 - 129, figs. 1 - 4." type="journal article" year="1994">Herbert (1994)</bibRefCitation>
. “L’Ile de 
<collectingCountry box="[634,713,1725,1749]" name="France" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">France</collectingCountry>
” is the former name of 
<collectingCountry box="[997,1109,1725,1749]" name="Mauritius" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Mauritius</collectingCountry>
, while under French control during the 18 
<superScript attach="left" box="[300,312,1761,1775]" fontSize="6" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">th</superScript>
century. Locality is 
<collectingCountry box="[541,654,1764,1788]" name="Mauritius" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Mauritius</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
